  <summary date="2015-02-25T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Food and Drug Administration Safety Over Sequestration Act of 2015 

This bill amends the Balanced Budget and Emergency Deficit Control Act of 1985 to exempt certain Food and Drug Administration user fees from sequestration. Sequestration is a process of automatic, usually across-the-board spending reductions under which budgetary resources are permanently cancelled to enforce specific budget policy goals.</summary>
